'From Squeak 2.1 of June 30, 1998 on 14 August 1998 at 1:08:34 pm'!"Change Set:		ExtensionInits-diDate:			14 August 1998Author:			Dan IngallsInit morphic extensions so that boolean accessors do not need to test for nil.This makes a substantial difference in how fast those accesses run.A doit at the end converts all extant instances."!!Morph methodsFor: 'extended access' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 12:55'!assureExtension	extension == nil ifTrue: [extension _ MorphExtension new initialize]! !!MorphExtension methodsFor: 'named access' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 13:07'!isPartsDonor	^ isPartsDonor! !!MorphExtension methodsFor: 'named access' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 13:07'!locked	^ locked! !!MorphExtension methodsFor: 'named access' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 13:07'!sticky	^ sticky! !!MorphExtension methodsFor: 'named access' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 13:07'!visible	^ visible! !!MorphExtension methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 12:55'!initialize	"Init all booleans to default values"	locked _ false.	visible _ false.	sticky _ false.	isPartsDonor _ false.! !!MorphExtension methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'di 8/14/1998 13:01'!initializeExtant	"Init all booleans to default values"	locked == nil ifTrue: [locked _ false].	visible == nil ifTrue: [visible _ false].	sticky == nil ifTrue: [sticky _ false].	isPartsDonor == nil ifTrue: [isPartsDonor _ false].! !"Postscript:Update all existing MorphExtensions.Executable statements after this comment quote..."MorphExtension allInstancesDo: [:e | e initializeExtant].MorphExtension removeSelector: #initializeExtant.!